Package sample.Model

Class Coffee

java.lang.Object
sample.Model.MenuItem
sample.Model.Coffee
All Implemented Interfaces:
Customizable
public class Coffee
extends MenuItem
implements Customizable
The Coffee class handles all operations relating to manipulating coffees, including adding and removing add-ins to the coffee, changing its quantity, and calculating its price.
